<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.5; }
        .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
        h2 { color: #2c3e50; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .info { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4a7fd7; }
        .info p { margin: 8px 0; }
        .footer { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Contract signed – Skill Bridge</h2>
        <p>A sponsorship contract has been signed and the PDF has been generated.</p>
        <div class="info">
            <p><strong>Sponsor:</strong> {{ sponsor_hackathon.sponsor.name }}</p>
            <p><strong>Hackathon:</strong> {{ sponsor_hackathon.hackathon.title }}</p>
            <p><strong>Contribution:</strong> {{ sponsor_hackathon.contributionType }} – {{ sponsor_hackathon.contributionValue|number_format(2) }} TND</p>
            <p><strong>Signed on:</strong> {{ signed_at|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</p>
        </div>
        <p>You can view and manage assignments in the back office.</p>
        <div class="footer">This is an automated notification from Skill Bridge.</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
